videos.headline: Jordan Hawkins drains the sweet up-and-under bucket for UConn
videos.description: Jordan Hawkins is smooth as silk as he glides through the paint to knock down the up-and-under basket for the Huskies.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jordan Hawkins drains the sweet up-and-under bucket for UConn) 2022/12/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Alex Karaban pulls up and knocks down the 3 for UConn
videos.description: Alex Karaban drains the three from the wing to extend the Huskies' lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Alex Karaban pulls up and knocks down the 3 for UConn) 2022/12/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Showtime! Andre Jackson steals the rock and slams it home
videos.description: Andre Jackson Jr. has the crowd on its feet as he steals the rock then spins and goes behind the back to finish with the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Showtime! Andre Jackson steals the rock and slams it home) 2022/12/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Andre Jackson throws it down with authority for UConn
videos.description: Andre Jackson Jr. gathers the rock and slams it home for the Huskies.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Andre Jackson throws it down with authority for UConn) 2022/12/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: C.J. Delancy rocks the rim for Long Island
videos.description: C.J. Delancy elevates and throws down a powerful jam for the Sharks.

videos.headline: Hassan Diarra makes no-look dime to Alex Karaban for a UConn slam
videos.description: Hassan Diarra dishes a sweet no-look dime to Alex Karaban for a Huskies flush.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hassan Diarra makes no-look dime to Alex Karaban for a UConn slam) 2022/12/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Andrew Hurley steals the rock and lays it in to extend UConn's lead
videos.description: Andrew Hurley steals the ball and lays in the basket to give the Huskies a 114-57 lead.
